一、課程目標：
透過個案討論介紹生產管理在企業管理研究中之背景概念、使用技術、應用範圍以及其重要性。



二、資源需求評估：




三、先修課程：




四、課程綱要：
The      
course provides an introduction to the concepts and analytic methods that      
are useful in understanding the management of a firm's operations. The      
level of analysis varies considerably from operations strategy, to daily      
control of production processes and inventory. Related topics will be discussed      
through cases associated with Decision Making, Forecasting, Production      
and Service Design, Aggregate Planning, Inventory Management, MRP, JIT,      
Scheduling, Waiting Lines, Quality Assurance, Logistics Management.



五、教學要求進行方式之建議：The      
class will be in a discussion orientation.




