一、課程目標：
This lecture is aimed to explore the properties of derivatives 
that are commonly encountered in practice, and to provide a theoretical framework within which all derivatives can be 
properly valued and hedged.



二、資源需求評估：
Matlab/Gauss software




三、先修課程：




四、課程綱要：
1.An introduction to derivatives 
  2.The market mechanics of derivatives trading 
  3.Ito's lemma, stochastic calculus, and martingale processes 
  4.Option pricing theory 
  5.Risk management 
  6.Numerical procedures 
  7.Exotic options 




五、教學要求進行方式之建議：
1.The lecturer uses textbooks and journal papers. 
  2.Students give presentations and take examinations.




